https://www.linuxfromscratch.org/blfs/view/stable/general/python3.html
The Python 3 package contains the Python development environment. It is useful for object-oriented programming, writing scripts, prototyping large programs or developing entire applications.
Python 3 was installed in LFS. The only reason to rebuild it here is if optional modules are needed, or to upgrade this package.

Use this script to upgrade python3 to include etras like the sqlite module and idle
